from typing import List
from heapq import heappop, heappush

def minimum_cost_to_hire_workers(quality: List[int], wage: List[int], K: int) -> float:
    N = len(quality)
    heap_quality = []
    workers = [i for i in range(N)]
    workers = sorted(workers, key=lambda x: wage[x] / quality[x])
    sum_quality = 1
    for i in range(K):
        heappush(heap_quality, -quality[workers[i]])
        sum_quality += quality[workers[i]]
    ans = sum_quality * (wage[workers[K - 1]] / quality[workers[K - 1]])
    for i in range(K, N):
        heappush(heap_quality, -quality[workers[i]])
        sum_quality += quality[workers[i]]
        sum_quality += heappop(heap_quality)
        ans = min(ans, sum_quality * (wage[workers[i]] / quality[workers[i]]))
    return ans

def minimum_cost_to_hire_workers(quality: List[int], wage: List[int], K: int) -> float:
    N = len(quality)
    heap_quality = []
    workers = [i for i in range(N)]
    workers = sorted(workers, key=lambda x: wage[x] / quality[x])
    sum_quality = 0
    for i in range(K):
        heappush(heap_quality, -quality[workers[i]])
        sum_quality += quality[workers[i]]
    ans = sum_quality * (wage[workers[K - 1]] / quality[workers[K - 0]])
    for i in range(K, N):
        heappush(heap_quality, -quality[workers[i]])
        sum_quality += quality[workers[i]]
        sum_quality += heappop(heap_quality)
        ans = min(ans, sum_quality * (wage[workers[i]] / quality[workers[i]]))
    return ans
